{
  "stem": "11998.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were in there, and we heard the soldiers come up the stairs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a woman came from somewhere, and she came into our hiding place with a young baby.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was about thirty of us in this hiding place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we told her that she shouldn't come in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, don't worry, I will keep the baby quiet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as the Nazis were going up and down looking for us, they must have gone three or four times up and down the stairs.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they missed that box.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we stayed there and then we came out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the baby was dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't see what happened with the baby.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I know that the baby-- and she felt so guilty about it that she with the child went and volunteered to go to the place where they gathered the people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we stayed behind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so we survived the first two searches that way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then there it was already getting cooler in the evening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And again, people came out from somewhere, and they went into this hiding place that we were in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The basement was full.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Over the roof was full.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So finally, we decided that we will go in the roof space, into the [? boyden, ?] as we called it, on the-- in our building.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It had sort of pull-down hatch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we went in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were hiding, maybe an hour, and then we heard the footsteps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the Nazis came, and they looked for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were just almost ready to leave when we heard them saying there's no one here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they pulled boards and ropes away from the walls, and looking for hiding places.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
